{"tid":2385831,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【私樓供應】一手住宅潛在供應維持9.2萬伙 去年私樓施工量1.18萬伙 按年跌36%","createTime":"2021-01-29T08:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T03:58:16.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"50771b13a6e84fe89ed28a590e7d3ccb297f2513","tid":2385831,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"【私樓供應】一手住宅潛在供應維持9.2萬伙 去年私樓施工量1.18萬伙 按年跌36%<br />\n10:15 2021/01/29<br />\n<br />\n&quot;運輸及房屋局今公布，截至今年第四季的未來3至4年的一手私人住宅供應量維持9.2萬個單位，較上一季的9.2萬伙維持不變，繼續在近4年低位橫行......<br />\n<br />\n......第4波疫情爆發，或影響新建項目審批及施工進度，上季私樓施工量只有200伙，按季急跌94%，2020年全年施工量則只有11800伙，按年跌36%，並且創2011年以來新低水平。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2865716/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%819.2%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99%20%20%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E9%87%8F1.18%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99%20%20%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E8%B7%8C6%E6%88%90?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2865716%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%2585%25E6%25BD%259B%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%25819.2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BC%2599%2520%2520%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%2587%258F1.18%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BC%2599%2520%2520%25E6%258C%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B7%258C6%25E6%2588%2590%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=51930a1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2865716/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%819.2%E8%90%AC%E4%BC%99%20%20%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E6%96%BD%E5%